\c 128
\s Ukubusiswa komuntu oqotho
\d Ingoma yokwenyuka
\p
\v 1 Ubusisiwe wonke oyesabayo iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + Hlab. 112.1.\x*\x + Hlab. 119.1. Zaga 8.32.\x*, ohamba endleleni zayo\x + Hlab. 119.1. Zaga 8.32.\x*.
\v 2 Ngoba uzakudla umsebenzi wezandla zakho\x + Isa. 3.10. Hlab. 109.11.\x*; uzathokoza, njalo kuzakuba kuhle kuwe\x + Isa. 3.10. Hlab. 109.11.\x*.
\v 3 Umkakho uzakuba njengevini elithelayo\x + Hez. 19.10.\x* emaceleni endlu yakho\x + Amos 6.10.\x*, abantwana bakho bazakuba njengamahlumela omhlwathi bezingelezele itafula lakho\x + Hlab. 144.12. Hlab. 52.8.\x*.
\v 4 Ngoba khangela, ngokunjalo izabusiswa indoda eyesabayo iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 5 IN\nd kosi\nd* izakubusisa\x + Hlab. 134.3.\x* iseZiyoni, njalo ubone okuhle kweJerusalema insuku zonke zempilo yakho\x + Hlab. 134.3.\x*\x + Hlab. 20.2. 135.21.\x*,
\v 6 yebo, uzabona abantwana babantwana bakho\x + Zaga 17.6. Jobe 42.16.\x*. Ukuthula kakube phezu kukaIsrayeli\x + Hlab. 125.5.\x*!